cos you cut off his thumb,

51:56.950 --> 51:59.950
or you cut off his thumb,

52:00.000 --> 52:02.400
cos you knew
he was going to sell you out.

52:06.600 --> 52:08.150
Possibility one-- reason.

52:10.300 --> 52:12.550
