52:12.600 --> 52:14.800
witchcraft.

52:18.800 --> 52:20.950
Leave this body
where it will be found.

52:22.650 --> 52:24.150
You can keep the heart.

52:26.450 --> 52:28.150
Goodnight.

52:45.550 --> 52:46.900
The devil's here.

